<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772765>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Comparison of typical-looking O. monilis (A), O. elegans sp. nov. (B), O. picta sp. nov. (C), and O. lineata sp. nov. (D). Photos: Conrad Hoskin." ;
