<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772777>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Holotype of O. picta sp. nov. (QM J83038; Lowestoff Rd, Coomburragee Station, Queensland). Photo: Conrad Hoskin." ;
